ry beginning of this story.  A new drug that combines a gut-hormone-mimicki=
ng peptide with a small molecule and targets the brain cells controlling ap=
petite has shown promising results and may potentially outperforming existi=
ng GLP-1s.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-hei=
ght: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The novel drug employs a &#8220;Trojan Hors=
