within a gut-hormone-mimicking peptide used in GLP-1s. This allows the drug=
 to specifically target and act on neurons in the brain that regulate appet=
ite, potentially enhancing weight-loss effects while minimizing side effect=
s. We&#8217;re still only working with mice here, but damn, those are some =
skinny mice. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-=
